bio: Ⓥ • NYC ⋆ Education Content & Training Manager @hauslabs by Lady Gaga ⋆ ♥ @mattwmurray

social_posts.post_text: So this mornin’ I took a mascara wand to a little “sunstone” #hauslabs bio-radiant gel powder highlighter and mixed it with “Secondary” @hauslabs lip oil.. now we have hydration station meets disco ball & I’m obsessed!! ❤️‍🔥✨

Whenever I used to wear this thrifted sweater around my Nana she would call me a “fashion plate”. 🥹 Having a love affair with using @hauslabs eyeliners in “navy matte” & “onyx gold shimmer” mixed together to create a Smokey eye. Lip is #hauslabs “rosewood shine” atomic shake lip lacquer. Skin: @hauslabs triclone skin tech foundation. I’m shade 100 light with “power sculpt” velvet bronzer in light level 3. Brows are @meltcosmetics new “max hold” brow gel (which is bananas amazing) and #meltcosmetics “perfectionist brow pen”.
Possible in-coming straight hair era? TBD
Lookin’ like a dad from the 1980s walkin’ into the woods.
Casually camouflaged. ❤️‍🔥🌲
I think I might be officially entering my straight hair era? Lip is @hauslabs Hy-power pigment paint in “scarlet”

Added a pop of brightness to my snowy day yesterday with @themobbeauty x @jessicahazemua cream clay shadow in M104. I paired it with @hauslabs Eco Liner in “Cocoa matte” and buffed and blended the hell out of it with a bit of “Level 4” power sculpt velvet bronzer and @tower28beauty mascara. Brows are #hauslabs dark brown pencil with @meltcosmetics brow gel on top. (Truly the longest holding and best brow gel I’ve ever used). Lip is #meltcosmetics “nudist” lip liner with “mauve matte” le monster lip crayon and a little “secondary” PHD lip oil on top. Skin is #hauslabs foundation with @hourglass stick concealer & #mobbeauty cream blush on top. #crueltyfreebeauty #cleanbeauty

I’m really in love with the long wearing formula and versatility of the #haus Hy-power pigment paints. Today I challenged myself to do my lips and eyes and brows only using 4 shades of @hauslabs paints. I used white onyx, blush, cocoa matte and black onyx. My Dreamy hair/ hair cut by @crybabyhairartistry.
every once and awhile you’re just inspired to shave off the tails of your brows and live a straight brow life for awhile.. or is that just me? apologies for the gloomy parking garage photo moment.

Utilizing a good smokey eye to hide what a snoozy little slug I am. (@hauslabs pigment paints in beige, cocoa matte & onyx - lip is #hauslabs “Sepia Shine”atomic shake lip lacquer with @meltcosmetics “nudist” lip pencil)
back to the hotel & immediately into soft clothes. #staymild

I haven’t been able to stop thinking about the stunning look that @sarahtannomakeup created on @ladygaga last night for the Oscars. I had to try and recreate it!! Using all @hauslabs of course. #hauslabs

Heading in store today, and I couldn’t remember the last time I’ve worn silver eyeshadow.. But thanks to TikTok trends I’ve been influenced. Hope you have a wonderful day, & please kiss your pet on the forehead for me, thank you. 💚

I have been looooving a high ponytail recently. & I switched most of my skincare to @olehenriksen a few months ago, so far my skin has been very happy with it! Lips are @hauslabs Atomic Shake in “Rose Shine” 🐸

What’s your favorite snack? Mine is popcorn, on the stove with a little olive oil, salt & garlic powder. Also here’s my Newest brow regiment; @hauslabs pencil in “noir” sketched lightly to s create the shape & @nyxcosmetics thickening brow mascara in black to make them stand nice and straight haha and a little “lift and snatch” brow tint pen in “espresso” to add some faux hair strokes. Lips is my favorite @hauslabs Atomic Shake lip lacquer in “rose” 💚🐸 #hauslabs #nyxcosmetics
@hauslabs pigment paint in “onyx” is my fav black eyeliner. @meltcosmetics lip in “muse” is like a freakin’ mood ring on your lips.

A continuous obsession to get that glass like skin. Featuring @hauslabs triclone skin tech foundation,  dragonfruit daze blush & rose quartz bio-radiant gel highlighter. Set with my favorite setting spray @onesize “preserve the serve, luminous”.
Quite possibly the coolest restroom I’ve ever seen.
Looking like I’m casually photoshopped into the poppy super bloom, but it was real life! Woke up early to check it out with @ikeara before heading to the airport back to NYC this past weekend.
The @hauslabs studio has the best selfie lighting.
I couldn’t pick just one of the new @hauslabs “Neutrals” Le Monster lip crayons, so I just wore all 4!! (Maple, blush, honey & mahogany)
Living in a perpetual state of monochrome greens.
My son is not pleased. #adoptdontshop
A little Matchy-Matchy moment. Lip is @hauslabs le monster crayon “mahogany” with “tint” lip oil on top.
Freakin’ chill zone outside today, but I’m loving this long wearing metallic lip. Wearing @hauslabs Le Monster crayon in “Mahogany” & “Burgundy Shimmer” Hy-power pigment paint. #hauslabs

just a baby.
“Secret pajamas” my essential 2023 summer wardrobe for this bananas humidity. Easy, breezy, vintage pj’s.
